    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#6119\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">glacier</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>1744年，源自法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">glacier</span>（16世纪），来自萨瓦方言 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">glacière</span> “移动的冰块”，源自古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">glace</span> “冰”，来自通俗拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">*glacia</span>（源头还包括古普罗旺斯语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">glassa</span>，意大利语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">ghiaccia</span>），来自拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">glacies</span> “冰”，可能源自 PIE 词根 <a href=\"/cn/word/*gel-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *gel- \" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">*gel-</a> “冷； 结冰”。德语瑞士形式 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">gletscher</span> 也曾在英语中使用（1764年）。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
  ],
  "relate": [
    {
      "title": "*gel-<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\"></div>",
      "html": "<p>原始印欧语根，意为“冷； 冻结”。</p><p>它构成或部分构成以下单词： <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of chill \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/chill\">chill</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cold \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cold\">cold</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of congeal \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/congeal\">congeal</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cool \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cool\">cool</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of gel \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/gel\">gel</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of gelatine \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/gelatine\">gelatine</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of gelatinous \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/gelatinous\">gelatinous</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of gelato \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/gelato\">gelato</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of gelid \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/gelid\">gelid</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glace \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glace\">glace</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glacial \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glacial\">glacial</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glaciate \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glaciate\">glaciate</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glaciation \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glaciation\">glaciation</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glacier \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glacier\">glacier</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glaciology \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glaciology\">glaciology</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glacis \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glacis\">glacis</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of jell \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/jell\">jell</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of jelly \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/jelly\">jelly</a>。</p><p>它是假设的来源/其存在的证据由以下单词提供：拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">gelare</i> “冻结”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">gelu</i> “霜”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">glacies</i> “冰”； 古英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cald</i> “冷，凉”，德语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kalt</i>。</p>"
